OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fincreasing from the west through the
OL,7,Fevening, which may bring some light
OL,8,Fdrizzle on higher hills. A mild night
OL,9,Fexpected with some places not dropping
OL,10,Fbelow double figures. Light
OL,11,Fsouthwesterly winds gradually
OL,12,Fincreasing towards dawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA cooler and more changeable
OL,15,Fday on Thursday, with a band of patchy
OL,16,Frain moving eastwards through the
OL,17,Fmorning. Clearing in the afternoon
OL,18,Fleaving sunny spells and blustery
OL,19,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
